_sText:
This is a remake of the classic zm map "zm wearhouse redux"


Background:
This map is a small based zombie mod map that has a mario theme to it. There are many places to hide and camp with buddies. Hope you survive!

Support:
Cubemaps, FPS (Hints/Skips, Area Portals), 64 Spawnpoints

Change Log:
  • [ADJUSTED] - Textures
